                  <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/31652541/#comments">回应</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;
                  2014-05-19 12:43
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </li>
      
      <li class="ctsh clearfix" data-cid="31652497">
        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/iveramo/"><img src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/user_normal.jpg" alt="[已注销]" class="" /></a>
